copy or link this folder on a server so that it is available as 'http://localhost/upms'

create a database ox_upms and load the data from source upms/ox_upms.sql

edit the upms/config.ini.php to set your database username and password

test server functionality: install openx and browse to openx_hostname/www/devel/upgrade/

test schema editor integration: install openx and browse to openx_hostname/www/devel/schema/

see ticket OX-1507 for TO DO list
